OL,3,CReligious hate crimes up by 25% in a
OL,4,Cyear following Israel-Hamas conflict
OL,6,FSince the conflict began just over a
OL,7,Fyear ago, there has been an outpouring
OL,8,Fof protesters in cities across
OL,9,FBritain, and a number of arrests over
OL,10,FIslamophobic and antisemitic incidents.
OL,12,FIn the year to March 2024, religious
OL,13,Fhate crimes recorded by police stood
OL,14,Fat 10,484 offences, compared to 8,370
OL,15,Fthe previous year.
OL,17,FThis is the highest annual count in
OL,18,Fthese offences since the hate crime
OL,19,Fcollection began in the year ending
OL,20,FMarch 2012.
